Final Fantasy Mystic Quest "A Terrible Secret" Randomizer
Version:    3
Date:       July 21, 2016
URL:        https://github.com/abyssonym/terriblesecret
Contact:    https://twitter.com/abyssonym
            https://www.twitch.tv/abyssonym

--- HOW TO USE ---
Running the randomizer:
    Windows users may use the executable file, "ffmq_terrible_secret.exe". Other users, please run "randomizer.py" using Python version 2.7.

Source rom file:
    This randomizer requires the North American SNES Final Fantasy Mystic Quest version 1.1 rom. The rom used for testing had the following verification hash.
    MD5 - f7faeae5a847c098d677070920769ca2

Flags:
    Input the following flags to customize your randomization experience.

    c  Randomize character stats.
    m  Randomize enemy stats.
    t  Randomize treasure.

Seed value:
    Input a seed value here, or leave it blank if you don't care.

Output files:
    The randomizer will output a new, randomized rom with the seed in the filename.

